<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "ASLAP70A7226025" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Kontrola ovládača regulácie teploty
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "ASLAP70A7226024">Demontáž a montáž ovládača regulácie teploty:Automatický typ</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nastavte rameno na ovládač a skontrolujte, či rameno funguje plynule, keď je napätie akumulátora vedené k svorkám konektora ovládača (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<title>
Činnosť ovládača riadenia teploty
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A722009V.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.766mm" ver = "01" gw = "197" gh = "113"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomocou ohmmetra odmerajte odpor medzi svorkou „3“”a svorkou „5“ konektora ovládača (1) v každej polohe ramena.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Odpor ovládača riadenia teploty
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.312in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.147in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Poloha ramena
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Odpor (25 &#176;C (77 &#176;F))
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
MAX COOL [a]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Približne 2,4 k&#937;
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
MAX HOT [b]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Približne 4,8 k&#937;
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pomocou ohmmetra odmerajte odpor medzi svorkou „1“ a svorkou „3“.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Ak nie je výsledok kontroly taký, ako je špecifikované, ovládač riadenia teploty vymeňte.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
